    {
      "kind": "content",
      "content": [
        {
          "anchor": "discussion",
          "level": 2,
          "text": "Discussion",
          "type": "heading"
        },
        {
          "type": "paragraph",
          "inlineContent": [
            {
              "type": "text",
              "text": "A call to the function "
            },
            {
              "type": "codeVoice",
              "code": "MPAllocateTaskStorageIndex"
            },
            {
              "type": "text",
              "text": " returns an index number that is common across all tasks in the current process. You can use this index number in calls to  "
            },
            {
              "type": "reference",
              "isActive": true,
              "identifier": "doc://com.apple.documentation/documentation/coreservices/1585626-mpsettaskstoragevalue"
            },
            {
              "type": "text",
              "text": "  and  "
            },
            {
              "type": "reference",
              "isActive": true,
              "identifier": "doc://com.apple.documentation/documentation/coreservices/1585589-mpgettaskstoragevalue"
            },
            {
              "type": "text",
              "text": "  to set a different value for each task using the same index. "
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "type": "paragraph",
          "inlineContent": [
            {
              "type": "text",
              "text": "You can think of the task storage area as a two dimensional array cross-referenced by the task storage index number and the task ID. Note that since the amount of per-task storage is determined when the task is created, the number of possible index values associated with a task is limited."
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "type": "paragraph",
          "inlineContent": [
            {
              "type": "text",
              "text": "Also see the function  "
            },
            {
              "type": "reference",
              "isActive": true,
              "identifier": "doc://com.apple.documentation/documentation/coreservices/1585649-mpdeallocatetaskstorageindex"
            },
            {
              "type": "text",
              "text": ". "
            }
          ]
        }
      ]
    }
